OL,6,FA thief who murdered a delivery driver
OL,7,Fas he tried to stop his van being
OL,8,Fstolen has been jailed for at least 30
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FMark Ross dragged Claudiu Carol-
OL,12,FKondor, 42, along the road at speeds
OL,13,Fof up to 60mph as he clung to the
OL,14,Fpassenger door of the van during the
OL,15,Fincident in Leeds.
OL,17,FHe collided with two parked cars,
OL,18,Fcausing Mr Kondor catastrophic
OL,19,Finjuries. Mr Kondor died at the scene.
