OL,3,CThief who murdered Amazon delivery
OL,4,Cdriver jailed for life
OL,6,FOn Friday Ross, 32, was jailed for
OL,7,Flife with a minimum term of 30 years
OL,8,Fat Leeds Crown Court.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Mr Kondor's fiancee
OL,11,FMariana Gheorghe said: "I don't know
OL,12,Fhow I will live without him,
OL,13,Feverything seems so difficult to me.
OL,14,FI'm still shocked and confused about
OL,15,Feverything that happened."
