OL,6,FDuring the trial the jury heard Mr
OL,7,FKondor had been delivering a package
OL,8,Fto an address in Alliance Street,
OL,9,FArmley, on the evening of 20 August
OL,10,Flast year when Mark Ross jumped into
OL,11,Fthe driver's seat of his silver Ford
OL,12,FTransit Cargo van.
OL,14,FHe drove off at speed, swerving from
OL,15,Fside to side.
OL,17,FCCTV footage played in court showed Mr
OL,18,FKondor hanging onto the van through an
OL,19,Fopen door as Ross travelled along
OL,20,FWingate Road.
