OL,4,Cdriver jailed for life
OL,6,FSentencing Ross, judge Mr Justice Goss
OL,7,Fsaid: "Claudiu Carol-Kondor must have
OL,8,Fbeen terrified in the last 45 seconds
OL,9,Fof his life as you ignored his pleas
OL,10,Fto stop and drove faster, dragging him
OL,11,Falong the road, causing him mental and
OL,12,Fphysical suffering."
OL,14,FThe court heard Mr Kondor had dreamed
OL,15,Fof owning his own van and bought it
OL,16,Fjust three weeks before he was killed.
