OL,6,FMs Gheorghe said he had a difficult
OL,7,Fupbringing in Romania and moved to
OL,8,FItaly at the age of 19, doing various
OL,9,Fjobs and working as a volunteer to
OL,10,Fhelp earthquake victims in 2009.
OL,12,FHe moved to England in 2019 and worked
OL,13,Fas a delivery driver and security
OL,14,Fguard, realising his dream of owning
OL,15,Fhis own van in July 2024.
OL,17,FMs Gheorghe said: "Of all his jobs he
OL,18,Fliked delivering the most. He enjoyed
OL,19,Fmeeting people, delivering parcels on
OL,20,Ftime and correctly.
