OL,6,F"When he finished work each day he was
OL,7,Fhappy to say he had done his best."
OL,9,FMs Gheorghe went on to say: "Both me
OL,10,Fand Claudiu were the kind of people
OL,11,Fwho like to work, who built a life on
OL,12,Fdreams and honest work on their own."
OL,14,FShe said she had been "forced to
OL,15,Freturn to Romania with a broken heart"
OL,16,Fafter his death.
OL,18,FA spokesperson for Amazon said: "Our
OL,19,Fthoughts remain with Claudiu's family,
OL,20,Ffriends and colleagues, who have all
OL,21,Fendured an unimaginable ordeal.
